ZH: 他昨天晚上吃了一碗热粥。
EN: He had a bowl of hot porridge last night.

ZH: 她喜欢在早上吃甜粥。
EN: She likes to eat sweet porridge in the morning.

ZH: 我们家常常做五谷杂粮粥。
EN: We often make five-grain porridge at home.

ZH: 他喜欢用姜和葱头来调味粥。
EN: He likes to season porridge with ginger and green onions.

ZH: 小孩子都爱吃鱼丸粥。
EN: Children all love to eat fish ball porridge.

ZH: 奶奶的鸡粥煮得特别香。
EN: Grandma's chicken porridge is particularly fragrant.

ZH: 他的腹泻好了以后，只能吃稀粥。
EN: After his diarrhea improved, he could only eat thin porridge.

ZH: 我们常常用红枣来熬粥。
EN: We often use red dates to cook porridge.

ZH: 年夜饭的时候，我们家必定会有一锅好粥。
EN: During the New Year's Eve dinner, our family always has a pot of good porridge.

ZH: 我最喜欢的早餐是绿豆粥。
EN: My favorite breakfast is mung bean porridge.

ZH: 他们在冬天的时候吃热粥。
EN: They eat hot porridge in the winter.

ZH: 古代的人们用糯米做粥来祭祀神灵。
EN: Ancient people used glutinous rice porridge to offer sacrifices to the gods.

ZH: 阿姨做的白粥非常清淡可口。
EN: The aunt's plain porridge is very light and delicious.

ZH: 外婆总是给我熬粥来养身。
EN: Grandma always cooks porridge for me to nourish my body.

ZH: 这家店的肉丸粥味道很不错。
EN: The meatball porridge at this restaurant tastes very good.

ZH: 我们用蔬菜和豆腐来烹饪粥。
EN: We cook porridge with vegetables and tofu.

ZH: 在病人住院时，医院会供应各种口味的粥。
EN: The hospital provides various flavors of porridge when patients are hospitalized.

ZH: 她一生病就只想吃粥。
EN: She only wants to eat porridge when she is sick.

ZH: 良好的稀粥要慢慢熬煮。
EN: Good thin porridge needs to be simmered slowly.

ZH: 大家都围着火盆吃着燕麦粥。
EN: Everyone gathered around the fire pit eating oat porridge.
